        <ul class="summary-list-global summary-list">
          <li>Maintained the custom API gateway service for the internal cloud infrastructure APIs.</li>
          <li>Maintained the custom authentication service for the internal cloud infrastructure.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="skill-bubble-global">
          <li><div>Go</div></li>
          <li><div>Cloud Infrastructure</div></li>
        </ul>
      </div><div class="experience-card hide" id="cinch">
